name: Christine Smith
description:
Buxom and shapely redhead stunner Christine Smith was born on April 6, 1979 in San Dimas, California. Christine was discovered by "Playboy" magazine when she accompanied a friend to a casting. Veteran photographer Stephen Wayda took some test photos of Smith, who was subsequently chosen by Hugh Hefner to be the Playmate of the Month in the December, 2005 issue of the famous men's magazine. She has posed for: Hooters calendar, Wilson Golf calendar, FireGirls, Muscle Magazine, Muscle Power and Nutrition, Easy Riders, Wicked Temptions, Atomix, Fever Magazine, and numerous others. Smith went on to appear in a couple of "Playboy" videos. She rehabilitates abused and unwanted animals. Christine has appeared in House Bunny, Bones, Last Comic Standing, CSI Miami, Celebrity Apprentice, Mad TV, Just Go With It, Walk Hard, Girls Next Door, Hancock, and recently Bad Teacher.

Trained on 1.5 base, but examples are on Analog Madness,

Skews NSFW as playmates tend to do, but SFW is easy too.

Defaults to redhead, but a few of the pictures were during her blonde phase. To ensure Redheadness, include redhead in your prompt.

If you have any comments/suggestions/criticism/suggestions for the next model please leave a comment or a review below.
